item.title: The Mine
item.description: The Mine is located at Drost Park in Maryville, IL with beatdowns on Monday, Wednesday, and Saturday. The Mine features a seven-acre lake, several pavilions, about three miles of asphalt walking trails, picnic tables, benches, playgrounds; everything a Q needs to run a perfect boot camp workout.

item.title: The Zoo
item.description: The Zoo is located at Tri-Township Park in Troy, IL with a beatdown on Wednesday and a ruck on Friday. The Zoo features a zoo.
